#Configure data recording tasks here.
# Formats:
# 	sample <sensor> every <number> <units> for <number> <units> 
#	OR
#	sample <sensor> continuously
# sensor can be one of:
# 	accelerometer
#	magnetometer
# 	bluetooth_proximity
# 	gps
# 	battery
# 	wifi
#	compass
# units can be one of:
# 	milliseconds
# 	seconds
# 	minutes
# number can be any non-negative long.
#

#JON CHIN:	samples wifi and bluetooth every 5 minutes

sample wifi every 5 minutes for 30 seconds
sample bluetooth_proximity every 5 minutes for 30 seconds

